// Main Content
.main
  section.warmup
    .warmup-inner.bound
      h2
        | Preschool. It’s not just for kids.
        span &#0153;
      p Study after study shows quality preschool is an educational springboard that prepares children to learn and succeed in education, their careers and in life.
      p Neuroscientists have found that early experiences – particularly from birth to age five– shape a child’s brain and development and can have long-lasting effects, ultimately preparing them for a brighter future.
      p: strong Preschool matters and LAUP is the trusted preschool authority in Los Angeles County.
  section.actions
    .actions-inner.bound
      h4: a.button.green href="http://www.laup.net/The-Research.aspx" Find a Local Preschool
